                  </hi> I am a hatter, and live in Great Suffolk-street—the prisoner was my journeyman—I missed four hats on Friday, 3rd Dec.—I went to the prisoner's lodging with a policeman, and gave the prisoner in charge of stealing the hats—these are mine (<hi rend="italic">produce.</hi>)</p>
